  "termsOfServiceTitle": "{appName} ውሎች of Service",
  "lastUpdatedVersion": "መጨረሻ የዘመነው፡ ሥሪት {version}",
  "tosSection1Title": "Acceptance of ውሎች",
  "tosSection1Para1": "By creating an account, accessing, or using the {appName} mobile application (\"the Service\"), you agree to be bound by these ውሎች of Service (\"ውሎች\"). If you do አይደለም agree to these ውሎች, you must አይደለም access or use the Service.",
  "tosSection1Para2": "The Service is provided by {producer} (\"we\", \"us\", or \"our\"). These ውሎች form a legally binding agreement between you and us.",
  "tosSection2Title": "ብቁነት እና መለያ",
  "tosSection2Para1": "You must be at least 13 years old to use the Service. If you are under 18, you represent that your parent or legal guardian has read and agreed to these ውሎች on your behalf.",
  "tosSection2Para2": "የመለያ ምስክርነቶችን ምስጢራዊነት የመጠበቅ እና በመለያዎ ስር ለሚከናወኑ ሁሉም ተግባራት እርስዎ ኃላፊነት አለብዎት። ማንኛውንም ያልተፈቀደ የመለያ አጠቃቀምዎን ወዲያውኑ ያሳውቁን።",
  "tosSection3Title": "ጤና Information — Not ህክምና Advice",
  "tosSection3Para1": "{appName} is a health companion application intended for informational and organizational purposes only. The Service is NOT a ህክምና device and አይደለም አይደለም provide ህክምና advice, ምርመራ, or treatment recommendations.",
  "tosSection3Para2": "The AI triage feature provides general guidance based on the symptoms you report. It is አይደለም a substitute for ባለሙያ ህክምና judgment. Always seek the advice of a ብቁ ጤና provider with any questions you may have regarding a ህክምና condition. Never disregard ባለሙያ ህክምና advice or delay seeking it because of something you read in this Service.",
  "tosSection3Para3": "In a ህክምና emergency, call your local emergency number (e.g. 911, 112) immediately. Do አይደለም rely on the Service for emergency response.",
  "tosSection4Title": "የአገልግሎቱን አጠቃቀም",
  "tosSection4Intro": "ላለማድረግ ተስማምተሃል፡-",
  "tosSection4Bullet1": "አገልግሎቱን ለማንኛውም ህገወጥ ዓላማ ይጠቀሙ;",
  "tosSection4Bullet2": "መሐንዲስን ለመቀልበስ፣ ለመበተን ወይም መተግበሪያውን ለመበተን መሞከር፤",
  "tosSection4Bullet3": "ተንኮል አዘል፣ አጭበርባሪ ወይም የአእምሯዊ ንብረት መብቶችን የሚጥስ ይዘት ይስቀሉ፤",
  "tosSection4Bullet4": "Interfere with the proper functioning of the Service or attempt to access ውሂብ belonging to other users;",
  "tosSection4Bullet5": "ያልተጠየቁ ግንኙነቶችን ወይም አይፈለጌ መልዕክት ለመላክ አገልግሎቱን ይጠቀሙ።",
  "tosSection5Title": "የደንበኝነት ምዝገባዎች እና ክፍያዎች",
  "tosSection5Para1": "Certain features of the Service require a paid subscription (\"Pro\" or \"ድርጅት\" plan). Subscription fees are billed monthly through the platform application store (Apple App Store or Google Play Store) subject to their respective terms.",
  "tosSection5Para2": "የአሁኑ የክፍያ ጊዜ ከማብቃቱ ቢያንስ 24 ሰዓታት በፊት ካልተሰረዙ የደንበኝነት ምዝገባዎች በራስ-ሰር ይታደሳሉ። የደንበኝነት ምዝገባዎን በማንኛውም ጊዜ በመሣሪያ ስርዓትዎ የመለያ ቅንብሮች በኩል ማስተዳደር ወይም መሰረዝ ይችላሉ።",
  "tosSection5Para3": "We may change subscription fees upon reasonable notice. Fee changes will አይደለም apply to your current billing period.",
  "tosSection6Title": "የእርስዎ ውሂብ",
  "tosSection6Para1": "You retain ownership of the health ውሂብ you submit to the Service. Our use of your ውሂብ is described in our ግላዊነት Policy, which is incorporated into these ውሎች by reference.",
  "tosSection6Para2": "You may export your ውሂብ at any time via the in-app ወደ ውጭ ላክ feature, and you may permanently delete your account and all associated ውሂብ via ቅንብሮች → ሰርዝ Account.",
  "tosSection7Title": "የክህደት ቃል",
  "tosSection7Para1": "አገልግሎቱ የሚቀርበው \"እንደሆነ\" እና \"እንደሚገኝ\" ያለ ምንም አይነት ዋስትናዎች፣ ግልጽም ሆነ የተዘዋዋሪ፣ ጨምሮ ነገር ግን ለሸቀጥ ዋስትናዎች ያልተገደበ፣ ለአካል ብቃት፣ ለአካል ብቃት።",
  "tosSection7Para2": "We do አይደለም warrant that the Service will be uninterrupted, error-free, or secure, or that the AI triage recommendations will be accurate or appropriate for your specific situation.",
  "tosSection8Title": "የተጠያቂነት ገደብ",
  "tosSection8Para1": "በህግ እስከተፈቀደው ከፍተኛው መጠን፣በምንም አይነት ሁኔታ {producer} ለማንኛውም ቀጥተኛ፣አጋጣሚ፣ልዩ፣ተከታታይ ወይም ለቅጣት ጉዳቶች፣ወይም የውሂብ መጥፋት፣ከእርስዎ ወይም ከተጠቃሚዎ ጋር በተዛመደ ማንኛውም አይነት ተጠያቂ አይሆንም። በዋስትና፣ ውል፣ ማሰቃየት ወይም በሌላ በማንኛውም የህግ ንድፈ ሃሳብ ላይ የተመሰረተ።",
  "tosSection9Title": "መቋረጥ",
  "tosSection9Para1": "You may stop using the Service and delete your account at any time via ቅንብሮች. We may suspend or terminate your access to the Service if you violate these ውሎች or if we reasonably believe we are required to do so by law.",
  "tosSection9Para2": "Upon termination, all licenses granted to you will end, and your ውሂብ will be deleted in accordance with our ግላዊነት Policy.",
  "tosSection10Title": "Changes to These ውሎች",
  "tosSection10Para1": "We may update these ውሎች from time to time. We will notify you of material changes via the app or by email. Continued use of the Service after changes take effect constitutes acceptance of the revised ውሎች.",
  "tosSection11Title": "አግኙ",
  "tosSection11Para1": "Questions about these ውሎች? አግኙ us at support@vitalseker.com.",
